# Static Routing 
show ip route = displays the routers IPv4 routing table 
ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 <next-hop> = configures a default route using next-hop IP
ip route <net> <mask> <next-hop> = creates a static route with a next-hop IP
ip route <net> <mask> <interface> = creates a static route using the exit interface
ip route <net> <mask> <interface> <next-hop> = creates a static route using both interface and next-hop

